<center><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#3333FF"><font size=+1>Benefits
of Distributed Project Management</font></font></font></b></center>

<blockquote>Let us see what benefits the startup companies can get from
Distributed Project Management.</blockquote>

<ol>
<ol>
<li>
<u>Document Management</u>: Document publication coordination and routing,
broadcast publishing.</li>

<br>&nbsp;
<li>
<u>Group Calendar/Scheduling</u>: staff and facilities calendar updates,
meeting management support, including meeting facilitation, and support
for virtual, remote or distributed meetings.</li>

<br>&nbsp;
<li>
<u>.roject Management</u>: workforce management and project coordination,
support for mobile working</li>

<br>&nbsp;
<li>
<u>Communication</u>: information sharing and threaded discussion forums,
including video- conferencing, collaborative working around a common 'table',
accessing remote and distributed applications, supporting key functions
business processes such as product development.</li>
</ol>

<p><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Following figure shows how a distributed project
management tool works.</ol>

